      "raceComments": "{\"comment\":\"6. RAZOR HAYZE recorded a one length win in a Maiden last time 25.73 at this track and trip and also jumping from the same draw. Can continue winning ways. 7. WIZARD SAID was prominent early from the tricky draw and stalked the lead before levelling up to score (25.24) at this track in a Maiden over 457m. Solid formlines coming through his last run. Will go close again if runs up to latest. 1. DOOGIE MCGRAW failed to feature last start after drifting back at Grafton, but prior to that won by 0.8 lengths at Grafton (25.44) beating Mystic Bloom in a Maiden on March 29. Got the money at his only try from this box. Cannot be taken lightly. 2. HELLO ELSA is new to this track but should be in the mix.\",\"runners\":[6,7,1,2],\"exclusive\":false}",
